een\", 20, \"blue\", 30, \"purple\", 40, \"yellow\"] as [Any])","        layer.circleRadius = NSExpression(forConstantValue: 3)","","        style.addLayer(layer)","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"DDSCircleLayerExample.png"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Map data from OpenStreetMap. Style uses OpenMapTiles."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"Vector Tile Sources","roleHeading":"Article"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/ddscirclelayerexample"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/LineStyleLayerExample":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adding an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to the map using a GeoJSON file."}],"role":"article","title":"Using GeoJSON with a line style layer","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/linestylelayerexample","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/LineStyleLayerExample"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNLineStyleLayer":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNLineStyleLayer"}],"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/M